  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The back pay and so on, and-- and threw me in the-- it's all-- all-- all in the book-- in a jeep and way down to Toronto.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they already ordered the other eight were-- I knew every one of them except one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were all members of our organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then I suspected, that must be something that we were on [INAUDIBLE] for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And sure enough, it-- it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there they assigned me-- assigned me all work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Took everything from my kit, my army kit, except the-- the things that you've-- you've got to get on yourself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You're not going to need it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they jammed us into-- into a car and then into a jeep, and out, started out to the east.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm coming to it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we talked as well, by god, they-- they taking us over to Montreal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or maybe-- maybe not to Montreal, maybe just to-- to Kingston.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as we come past Whitby, a couple-- a couple more miles, a dirt road, a farmer road just [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the jeep just tears up the dirt on dirt road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, where the hell are we going?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden we come to a-- came to a-- a huge sign there, huge sign.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This-- this-- this area, or this property-- how did it say-- is under the-- under the protection of national defense.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we looked at the sign or whatever, a-- a guard with a bayonet that we had to stop, but he knew that the-- the drivers and so on had opened up the gate and drived into.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it-- it was really a crummy place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, all the rough buildings and-- and structures and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
